HEADWORD: Kneepan
<hw>Knee"pan`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>A
roundish, flattened, sesamoid bone in the tendon in front of the knee
joint; the patella; the kneecap.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

